Build Dependencies
==================

To successfully build and install this application you need to have cmake 
with minimal version 2.8.12 including FindLua.cmake module.

For Lua scripting you need Lua and Tolua++ libraries for development.

Basic Installation
==================

Extract tarball and run following set of commands:

	mkdir build 
	cd build
	cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release ..
	make
	make install

- for disablin of LUA scripting support add following option:

	-DENABLE_LUA=OFF 

	E.g: cmake -DENABLE_LUA=OFF ..

Binary sjasmplus file will be placed in /usr/bin by default.

To change install directory prefix add following option with specified prefix:

	-DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX:PATH=/usr/local

	e.g: cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX:PATH=/usr/local ..
